00:41:07,603 --> 00:41:10,939
God, I hope he fits
in the trunk.

524
00:41:35,064 --> 00:41:36,665
Are you all right?

525
00:41:36,766 --> 00:41:39,768
I'm fine.
Let's do this.

526
00:41:55,351 --> 00:41:57,652
I suck.

