00:42:18,975 --> 00:42:21,543
Why didn't the real estate guy
tell you that?

535
00:42:21,611 --> 00:42:24,346
Because, Norman, people suck.

536
00:42:24,447 --> 00:42:27,649
I'll tell you, everyone
